creating Colaberry Logo 10

Steps

Adding Colaberry Logo

1.    Click on Insert from the Power Bi desktop Menu.

2.    Then click on Image

3.    Select the Image from the file

4.    General:  X - Position = 21, Y - Position = 19, Width = 109  and Height = 70
